797
01:26:34,574 --> 01:26:37,029
Sometimes, Comrade Nurse,
women have to wait.

798
01:26:37,903 --> 01:26:38,852
Right!

799
01:26:39,119 --> 01:26:40,745
Goodbye, honored Doctor.

800
01:26:41,838 --> 01:26:43,180
Want some advice?

801
01:26:43,278 --> 01:26:45,995
- Said the millstone to the barley.
